snippet.title: Voidtrain - Exclusive Official Release Date Trailer
snippet.description:
Check out this exclusive release date trailer for Voidtrain to take a tour of various locations, as well as see strange creatures, enemies, and more from this upcoming survival crafting FPS game. Voidtrain will be available on Steam on May 9, 2023. Wishlist it on Steam here if you're interested: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1159690/Voidtrain/

In Voidtrain, become a crew member of an Interdimensional Express Train! Discover a new world full of mysterious creatures, enemies and places. Upgrade and customize your train, gather new materials and build better weapons. Play solo or online сo-op with up to 4 people.

#IGN #GameTrailers
